result.title: Specialists Training Group and First Common Contest
result.content:
Welcome to Specialists training group.

This group is for ACM communities following the specialist training plan. Current participating acm communities:

  • GUC Community
  • AAST Community
  • FE-CU Community

Here we start with a common contest between the three communities. It will be about DP. You should have received an invitation to participate in the contest. If you didn't receive it, comment below. You can find the contest in the "contests" tab.

We will discuss the contest problems in the comments. Get ready!
